===Noun phrase===
'''[[general]] [[relativity]]'''

# {{physics}} A theory extending [[special relativity]] and uniformly accounting for [[gravity]] and accelerated [[frame of reference|frames of reference]], postulating that [[space-time]] curves in the presence of mass.

